00:55:25.410 --> 00:55:26.310 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:55:26.310 --> 00:55:26.960 align:middle line:90%
>>RAPPOPORT: Right?

00:55:26.960 --> 00:55:28.168 align:middle line:90%
That's when the answers come.

