00:55:51.330 --> 00:55:52.620 align:middle line:90%
He was creating something.

00:55:52.620 --> 00:55:54.050 align:middle line:90%
This was his art.

00:55:54.050 --> 00:55:56.290 align:middle line:84%
He built a stone and
